OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1777907466
OL,3,CMajor incident declared after two
OL,4,Cpeople die in an explosion near Bristol
OL,6,FA major incident has been declared in
OL,7,FSouth Gloucestershire and dozens of
OL,8,Fhomes evacuated after an explosion at
OL,9,Fa home in Frenchay.
OL,11,FPolice, ambulance crews and bomb
OL,12,Fdisposal experts were called to the
OL,13,Fhouse on Sterncourt Road at about
OL,14,F6.30am today (Sunday 3 May.)
OL,16,FTwo adults have died at the address
OL,17,Fand their families have been updated.
OL,19,FAvon and Somerset Police say they are
OL,20,Ffollowing 'well-rehearsed plans' in
OL,21,Fresponse to the incident.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
