CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1777907466
OL,3,CMajor incident declared after two
OL,4,Cpeople die in an explosion near Bristol
OL,6,FA police spokesperson said: "Our
OL,7,Fenquiries are at an early stage, but
OL,8,Fat this point we are not looking for
OL,9,Fanyone else in connection with this
OL,10,Fincident.
OL,12,F"Given the recent change to the UK
OL,13,Fthreat level, we would like to
OL,14,Freassure the public from the outset we
OL,15,Fare not treating this as a suspected
OL,16,Fterrorist incident."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
