PN,43103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1777907466
OL,3,CMajor incident declared after two
OL,4,Cpeople die in an explosion near Bristol
OL,6,FThey added: "We ask people not to
OL,7,Fspeculate around the circumstances and
OL,8,Fcontinue to encourage the public to
OL,9,Favoid the area while emergency
OL,10,Fservices respond to this incident."
OL,12,FOfficers are also carrying out
OL,13,Fenquiries at a property in Speedwell.
OL,15,FA cordon remains in place in Frenchay
OL,16,Fand dozens of people have been told to
OL,17,Fleave their homes. Many have been
OL,18,Ftaken to a local pub which is doubling
OL,19,Fas a rest centre.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
